## Detection
| Source | Event ID | Indicator |
|---|---|---|
| Windows Security Log | 4648 | Explicit credential use to unknown host |
| Wazuh Rule 100001 | level 10 | LLMNR poisoning — T1557.001 |

## Remediation
- Disable LLMNR via GPO:
  `Computer Configuration → Administrative Templates → Network → DNS Client → Turn off multicast name resolution → Enabled`
- Disable NBT-NS on all network adapters
- Enable SMB signing to prevent relay attacks